{"tid":2296022,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"I奶小田飛鳥大銀幕解放 擔心男主角無法一手掌握","createTime":"2020-11-22T07:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T08:09:41.000Z","uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c9e64b94cd0d9737e2ca130271cb0f3f8898cd","tid":2296022,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:13:20.000Z","msg":"寫真女星小田飛鳥憑著I罩杯巨乳打響名號，因大膽的作風及言談被稱之為「性感番長」，她首次登大銀幕的作品《焦燥》，挑戰大銀幕全裸演出，被問到在劇中「它」的表現如何，小田飛鳥笑說：「『它』才是本作的MVP！」甚至擔心飾演男主角的隆大介無法一手掌握。<br />\n<br />\n談到電影看點，小田飛鳥首推最後一幕床戲，必須完美詮釋出女主角紗弓的覺悟與對藤森的愛慕之情，對此她也坦言：「在拍攝當時我竭盡所能地表現，甚至做出超乎常理的舉動，因此我覺得那一幕是相當有看點的床戲！」<br />\n<br />\n劇情描述年邁的資產家藤森（隆大介 飾），在盛夏的墓園中遇見抱著母親骨灰的紗弓（小田飛鳥 飾），並對遊走在墓園中的她一見鍾情，而後在夜晚的公園中找到爛醉的紗弓進而拉近兩人的關係。從未見過生父的紗弓將藤森視為父親般敬愛，也漸漸愛上身為男人的他。某日，在藤森的邀請下造訪別墅的紗弓，發現一幅與自己容貌相似的神祕少女畫像。在暴風雨的夜晚中，由於不速之客襲來，藤森與紗弓的關係無法抑制般逐漸發狂。電影12月4日在台上映。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1CQPW7o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1CQPW7o.jpg&h=a413a505&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e37a2e0c0c60aa5c1c072006c995d8a249b2d89f","tid":2296022,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:17:59.000Z","msg":"奶呢?"},{"pid":"7619dcfa57b899a4e18b2bf8d7c0921ba3c7be2a","tid":2296022,"uid":331590,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DxU3gTQU8AMbrD3?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDxU3gTQU8AMbrD3%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=35cc636d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f819470e4596fa6a70f281ce777faef828305de0","tid":2296022,"uid":144001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"係咪即係old boy"},{"pid":"f7c59b594f778f6c9e554fbd9ab0f1eb4fbc19c7","tid":2296022,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T08:08:44.000Z","msg":"唔夠靚女所以我好認真睇篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66fb537fe3c513fabd988739311205ce20cb376d","tid":2296022,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T08:09:41.000Z","msg":"樣子不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}